Class DocumentGrammarBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.java.antlrgen.DocumentGrammarBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DocumentGrammarListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener

    public class DocumentGrammarBaseListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements DocumentGrammarListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of DocumentGrammarListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
